ford university's department barbara van schewick is an associate professor of law and helen l read more about barbara van schewick marvin ammori affiliate scholar marvin ammori is a leading first amendment lawyer and internet policy expert he was instrumental to the adoption of network neutrality rules in the us and abroad having been perhaps the nation's leading legal advocate advancing network neutrality and also instrumental to the defeat of the sopa and pipa copyright censorship bills read more about marvin ammori brief amicus curiae of professors jack m balkin jim chen lawrence lessig barbara van schewick and timothy wu urging that the fcc's order be afirmed author s barbara van schewick lawrence lessig publication date october 5 2009 publication type litigation brief read more about brief amicus curiae of professors jack m balkin jim chen lawrence lessig barbara van schewick and timothy wu urging that the fcc's order be afirmed official testimony at the federal communications commission's second public en banc hearing on broadband network management practices author s barbara van schewick publication date april 17 2008 publication type regulatory filing read more about official testimony at the federal communications commission's second public en banc hearing on broadband network management practices lawrence lessig statement broadband network management practices en banc public hearing stanford university palo alto ca 4 17 08 april 17 2008 read more about lawrence lessig statement broadband network management practices en banc public hearing stanford university palo alto ca 4 17 08 get involved follow us facebook twitter youtube flickr subscribe to email updates email address subscribe to rss feeds attend an event donate to cis other ways to get involved upcoming events apr 9 sopa pipa and internet freedom where do we go from here stanford law school apr 11 robot block party stanford university apr 18 cis speaker series privacy in the age of augmented realit